data.name: labelText.Text
data.value: Marina River is located in the Strandja Nature Park itself, next to the river itself. There you can get there by car and when you reach the destination you can park on the unguarded car park there. The eco path starts from the road Tsarevo - Malko Tarnovo, about 12 km from Tsarevo. In about 50 minutes you will need to cross the eco path in one direction.
